-5 cWSLWv"><aside class="sc-3ddd79c0-12 cmKAit"><div aria-hidden="true" class="rah-static rah-static--height-zero SidebarWrapper" style="height:0;overflow:hidden"><div><div class="sc-2e8621ab-0 jdutDe sc-3ddd79c0-7 jAbpEx"><a href="/users/peter-mumford-2" class="sc-2e8621ab-1 gnJVZv">Peter Mumford</a><span><p>has an MPhil and BA in Classics from the University of Cambridge. He is currently interning at Highgate, a strategic advisory firm. He is a member of Chatham House’s Common Futures Conversations programme and also works with USPUK, a non-profit organisation supporting displaced people from Ukraine and Afghanistan.</p></span></div><br/><div class="sc-3ddd79c0-9 evnbsV"><p>Edited by<a href="/users/samdresser" class="sc-2e8621ab-1 gnJVZv">Sam Dresser</a></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-fb580250-0 bUjhzA"><span>3,600<!-- --> words</span><span class="sc-fb580250-2 foyURG"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="17" height="17" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-save" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 3H7c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L5 21l7-3 7 3V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 15l-5-2.18L7 18V5h10v13z"></path></svg><span>Save</span></span></div><br/><div class="sc-5c8686bf-1 UhORy"><a class="sc-45649ee9-0 dKXLeq sc-5c8686bf-0 fFoFgq" href="/syndication?article_slug=how-russia-is-putting-the-ancient-scythians-to-war-in-ukraine&amp;article_name=Legacy%20of%20the%20Scythians&amp;author=Peter%20Mumford&amp;date=19%20March%202024"><span class="sc-45649ee9-1 cacrwE">Syndicate this <!-- -->essay</span></a></div><div class="sc-c3e98e6e-0 cziXAF sc-3ddd79c0-13 bBqJYi"><div class="sc-c3e98e6e-0 cziXAF"><div><br/></div><div class="sc-531dc212-0 gowMUU"><div><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" width="20px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-email" aria-hidden="true" class="sc-531dc212-1 hYsNZY"><path d="M22 6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2H4