" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" data-cy="icon-aeon-save" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17 3H7c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L5 21l7-3 7 3V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 15l-5-2.18L7 18V5h10v13z"></path></svg><span class="sc-d56bc236-4 gKlMxC">Save</span></div><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-3 iOJnhy eIqCxs">essay</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-2 iOJnhy llXHdp">Economic history</p></div><p class="sc-d56bc236-10 tdBWn">The southern gap</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-11 hYbLtW">In the American South, an oligarchy of planters enriched itself through slavery. Pervasive underdevelopment is their legacy</p><p class="sc-d56bc236-0 sc-d56bc236-12 iOJnhy dFhhBp">Keri Leigh Merritt</p></div><div class="sc-d56bc236-6 kQroYe"></div></div></a><a href="/essays/bernard-stieglers-philosophy-on-how-technology-shapes-our-world"><div class="sc-d56bc236-9 cKZvmh"><div type="essay" class="sc-82db9615-2 ldkvZH"><img alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, (max-width: 960px) 45vw, (max-width: 1440px) 30vw, 430px" srcSet="https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/832a2200-3ca4-48c5-8dcb-0c8688eb921b/essay-v2-final-gettyimages-1997669611.jpg?width=256&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 256w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/832a2200-3ca4-48c5-8dcb-0c8688eb921b/essay-v2-final-gettyimages-1997669611.jpg?width=384&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 384w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/832a2200-3ca4-48c5-8dcb-0c8688eb921b/essay-v2-final-gettyimages-1997669611.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 640w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/832a2200-3ca4-48c5-8dcb-0c8688eb921b/essay-v2-final-gettyimages-1997669611.jpg?width=750&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 750w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/832a2200-3ca4-48c5-8dcb-0c8688eb921b/essay-v2-final-gettyimages-1997669611.jpg?width=828&amp;quality=75&amp;format=auto 828w, https://images.aeonmedia.co/images/832a